<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IMF Gadget API - Documentation</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-light">
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center">🚀 IMF Gadget API - Documentation</h1>
        <p class="text-center">Use Postman or any API client to interact with the API.</p>
        
        <div class="card bg-secondary p-3">
            <h3>📌 Base URL</h3>
            <p><code>https://imf-c46r.onrender.com</code></p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
            <h2>🛠 API Endpoints</h2>
            
            <h3 class="mt-3">🔐 User Authentication</h3>
            <h4>📌 Register</h4>
            <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-3">POST /auth/register</pre>
            <p><strong>Request Body:</strong></p>
            <pre class="bg-light text-dark p-3">{
    "username": "agent007",
    "password": "securepassword"
}</pre>
            
            <h4>📌 Login</h4>
            <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-3">POST /auth/login</pre>
            <p><strong>Request Body:</strong></p>
            <pre class="bg-light text-dark p-3">{
    "username": "agent007",
    "password": "securepassword"
}</pre>
            <p><strong>Response:</strong> Returns a JWT token for authentication.</p>

            <h3 class="mt-3">📍 Get All Gadgets</h3>
            <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-3">GET /gadgets</pre>
            <p><strong>Headers:</strong> Authorization: Bearer &lt;your_token&gt;</p>
            <p><strong>Example:</strong></p>
            <pre class="bg-light text-dark p-3">curl -X GET -H "Authorization: Bearer &lt;your_token&gt;" https://imf-c46r.onrender.com/gadgets</pre>
            <p><strong>Response:</strong></p>
            <pre class="bg-light text-dark p-3">[
    { "id": "1", "name": "The Nightingale", "status": "Available", "successProbability": "87%" },
    { "id": "2", "name": "The Kraken", "status": "Deployed", "successProbability": "75%" }
]</pre>
            
            <h3 class="mt-3">➕ Add a New Gadget</h3>
            <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-3">POST /gadgets</pre>
            <p><strong>Headers:</strong> Authorization: Bearer &lt;your_token&gt;</p>
            <p><strong>Request Body:</strong></p>
            <pre class="bg-light text-dark p-3">{
    "name": "X-Ray Lens"
}</pre>
            
            <h3 class="mt-3">✏️ Update a Gadget</h3>
            <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-3">PATCH /gadgets/:id</pre>
            <p><strong>Headers:</strong> Authorization: Bearer &lt;your_token&gt;</p>
            <p><strong>Example Body:</strong></p>
            <pre class="bg-light text-dark p-3">{
    "status": "Deployed"
}</pre>

            <h3 class="mt-3">🗑 Remove (Decommission) a Gadget</h3>
            <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-3">DELETE /gadgets/:id</pre>
            <p><strong>Headers:</strong> Authorization: Bearer &lt;your_token&gt;</p>
            <p><strong>Note:</strong> This does not delete the gadget but marks it as "Decommissioned".</p>
            
            <h3 class="mt-3">💣 Self-Destruct a Gadget</h3>
            <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-3">POST /gadgets/:id/self-destruct</pre>
            <p><strong>Headers:</strong> Authorization: Bearer &lt;your_token&gt;</p>
            <p><strong>Response:</strong> Marks the gadget as "Destroyed" with an immediate timestamp.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>